translate ru SailorPath3_8aef9c8a:
    # "Days more had passed since then and Sarah's body had gradually recovered."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_0cc3c607:
    # "The daily work kept her muscles in a constant sore state, but having known true and complete exhaustion, Sarah now considered this muscle ache a minor inconvenience."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_77c38345:
    # "Belmont had given her perhaps a day's worth of respite, but not long after he had begun to use her body again."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_a0bea643:
    # "Sarah had eagerly welcomed it."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_ae8102a5:
    # "The punishment he had dished out on her had left more than just a physical effect."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_0b35cafe:
    # "It had reset the relationship between them. It made Sarah realize she had gotten too comfortable with the captain, mistaking her place on the ship."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_a38df348:
    # "With her new understanding Sarah began to submit herself to him fully."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_72d72c01:
    # "She followed his every order both on the ship and in bed. She kept reminding herself, he was the captain and she a deck hand."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_b6aa9109:
    # "There was no part of her body that she reserved from him, no act she wouldn't submit herself to."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_d2d32a9d:
    # "Even things that she cherished in private, she now gave up to him. She danced for him, and sang for him, revealing those parts she hid from anyone else."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_311c2474:
    # "Sarah had long accepted giving him her body, but she now gave him more than she had ever imagined."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_7a8f397b:
    # "Belmont pushed her, prodded. He tried things, to see where she would draw a line, but realized there were no lines left."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_83b413ba:
    # "Sarah had given herself fully to the captain and he seized every part of her."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_01d8c36b:
    # "In this new state, the two operated the ship and sailed it through mostly calm and quiet sea."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_eaf97bbd:
    # "For a moment, Sarah dreamed it might simply go on forever."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_88b5b6e9:
    # "No more land. No more people. Just a simple life that demanded nothing of her, only her willing submission. Life could be so easy."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_6724123c:
    # "But few things last, and so it was to her own surprise that Sarah felt a pain in her heart as she first laid eyes on the harbor of Rahayal."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_d2f05d78:
    # "Rahayal, the capital of Mythra, one of the greatest empires in all the world and with it, one of the greatest cities in all the world."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_46190e25:
    # "The capital of Mythra was famous for its countless marble columns, reaching out from the earth and holding above them the ceilings of some of the greatest wonders that ever were."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_55ca1ba7:
    # "One wonder in particular, dominated all other things in the city. The dark pyramid; the house of the Eternal Court."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_9992f0b3:
    # "It sat atop one of the larger hills that the city had been build on, towering over most everything else, and so alien in its design it almost looked as if some other culture had left it there."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_2248051a:
    # "Maybe they had. Sarah didn't know."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_4ca25a2d:
    # "In accordance with its wealth and power, the city was also swarming with people."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_500a1f89:
    # "This far out, the city and its people looked like a great ant hill, tiny dots climbing over one another, all busy with some task, who knew what."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_4d0896e0:
    # "Sarah stood out on the bow, staring at the marvel."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_1609e1e3:
    # s "It's..."
    s ""

translate ru SailorPath3_35dc9335:
    # cb "Yeah, took my breath away too first time I got here."
    cb ""

translate ru SailorPath3_bf936778:
    # s "It's beyond anything I ever saw."
    s ""

translate ru SailorPath3_d496d88c:
    # cb "You grew up in Rosanna, right?"
    cb ""

translate ru SailorPath3_e5f436b2:
    # "He liked to play clever. She had never told him as much, he was fishing for information. But Sarah was in no mood to play games."
