    # cb "They forgettin there's all sorts of worlds out there."
    cb ""

translate ru SailorPath3_234f2ead:
    # "Sarah kept looking as captain Belmont began to unrig the sails and fix the ropes."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_bf551f13:
    # "As they neared the opening to the harbor, the ship crawled to a slow and steady pace."
