    # "All around them, there were now ships in all sizes and styles, hailing from every corner of the world."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_a61ef131:
    # "It was a strange realization for Sarah, that the ship that had been her entire world for nearly two weeks, was in fact a laughably small one compared to most others."
