translate ru SailorPath3_2cd4012b:
    # "On each side, countless buildings and countless more people flanked the hills on which the city had been build."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_475b7591:
    # "They loomed over them, the way the sides of a canyon might."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_9a9a2957:
    # "With each turn, Belmont guided the ship down an increasingly smaller riverway, and the number of other boats and people slowly faded."
    ""

translate ru SailorPath3_ef9a5a9c:
    # "Still, even at its calmest, the city and its people outnumbered even the busiest street in Rosanna."
